title: Namibia Prime Lending Rate
description: Lending Rate in Namibia increased to 10 percent in October from 9.25 percent in September of 2022. Lending Rate in Namibia averaged 13.71 percent from 1991 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 24.20 percent in July of 1998 and a record low of 7.50 percent in August of 2020. This page provides - Namibia Lending Rate- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Bank of Namibia
